data.description: RANCH ALERT!! It's EASY living in this 2 bedroom home. VINYL siding, over sized double plus wide  driveway & central air.  Eat in kitchen has lots of counter space, double ovens, & plenty of cabinets.  Adjoining next to kitchen could be a formal dining or family room. Double closets in main bedroom.  You will find wood vaulted ceilings in the space the current owner is using as a living room. PLUS IT IS LOCATED BY EVERYTHING COOL HAPPENING. This home is right off of all major roads leading in all directions that makes which ever way you are traveling so accessible!
